clue: At the L.A. County Museum of Art, Stephanie Barron is a senior one of these in the Department of Modern Art

response: curator

clue: More so than a nanny, this female employee concentrates on teaching the children in a home, not chaperoning

response: a governess

clue: With a name from Latin for "copyist", this type of insurance specialist calculates risks & premiums

response: an actuary

clue: Longshoreman or this word that begins with a male name can be used for a worker who loads & unloads ships in a port

response: a stevedore

clue: Terms for shoemakers include cobbler & this more archaic one derived from a type of Spanish leather

response: a cordwainer

